king-from-home-is-making-people-lonelier-and-worsening-mental-health-a-study-suggests-180988938/</link><description>专家表示，调查结果并不意味着办公室授权是解决办法。相反，工作场所应该制定灵活的政策，允许员工选择他们想要工作的地方</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 19:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/working-from-home-is-making-people-lonelier-and-worsening-mental-health-a-study-suggests-180988938/</guid></item><item><title>你的狗是右撇子还是左撇子？根据一项新研究，这是如何解决这个问题的</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/is-your-dog-right-pawed-or-left-pawed-heres-how-to-figure-it-out-according-to-a-new-study-180988941/</link><description>研究人员设计了一系列测试来测量毛茸茸的朋友的偏侧性，这可能与行为、情绪和认知相关</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 19:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/is-your-dog-right-pawed-or-left-pawed-heres-how-to-figure-it-out-according-to-a-new-study-180988941/</guid></item><item><title>在人工智能的帮助下，一个家庭意识到他们在旧货店发现的神秘物品是一位伟大的苏格兰画家的肖像</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/with-help-from-ai-a-family-realized-their-mysterious-thrift-store-find-is-a-portrait-by-a-great-scottish-painter-180988948/</link><description>这幅油画是“苏格兰调色师”FCB Cadell的作品，刚刚在拍卖会上以超过25万美元的价格售出</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 17:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/with-help-from-ai-a-family-realized-their-mysterious-thrift-store-find-is-a-portrait-by-a-great-scottish-painter-180988948/</guid></item><item><title>研究人员意外发现人类更喜欢逆时针转动。但他们仍然不知道为什么</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/researchers-accidentally-discover-that-humans-prefer-to-turn-counterclockwise-180988939/</link><description>这种效应超越了文化、性别和惯用手等因素，让最初研究社交距离行为的科学家们摸不着头脑</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 16:30:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/researchers-accidentally-discover-that-humans-prefer-to-turn-counterclockwise-180988939/</guid></item><item><title>科学家发现世界上最大、最深的鲸鱼墓地，鲸